metadata.name: Ava 🌸
metadata.description:
Ava 🌸 is my very first open edition 👨‍🎨  
I do my best to create a portrait in modern style, trying to give you maximum emotion, creating a dynamic picture of light and color. 👌

Ava is a name that dates back to medieval times, with Germanic origins.  
It is an abbreviation of a Germanic name containing the first element aw-, of uncertain meaning.  
It also has Latin and Hebrew roots, meaning life.  
Ava is also a name in the Persian language meaning "voice or sound."  
📝  
Latin : Blooming  
Latin: Birdlike  
Hebrew: Life
